STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Donald HIGGS, a/k/a Kyle Beachum, Devoan Edwards, Lee Harold, Devin Higgs, Devon Higgs, Harold Lee and Ahmir Pierce, Defendant-Petitioner. C-29 September Term 2018
080808 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 12, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000660-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
